select 'GICS Industry' as SCHEME_NAME ,'GIND' as INDUST_CLASS_CD ,g.GICS_INDUSTRY_NM as INDUST_NAME ,g.GICS_INDUSTRY as INDUST_CD ,NULL as SECURITY_ID ,crd.EXTERNAL_SECURITY_IDENTIFIER from T_ODS_SEC s join T_ODS_CRD_SEC crd on s.ODS_SEC_ID = crd.ODS_SEC_ID join T_ODS_REF_GICS g on s.ODS_GICS_ID = g.ODS_GICS_ID and s.BBRG_YELLOW_KEY <> 'Muni' where s.ACTV_FLG = '1' and s.EXT_Sec_ID is not null
union
select 'GICS Industry Group' as SCHEME_NAME ,'GINDG' as INDUST_CLASS_CD ,g.GICS_INDUSTRY_GROUP_NM as INDUST_NAME ,g.GICS_INDUSTRY_GROUP as INDUST_CD ,NULL as SECURITY_ID ,crd.EXTERNAL_SECURITY_IDENTIFIER from T_ODS_SEC s join T_ODS_CRD_SEC crd on s.ODS_SEC_ID = crd.ODS_SEC_ID join T_ODS_REF_GICS g on s.ODS_GICS_ID = g.ODS_GICS_ID and s.BBRG_YELLOW_KEY <> 'Muni' where s.ACTV_FLG = '1' and s.EXT_Sec_ID is not null
union
select 'GICS Sector' as SCHEME_NAME ,'GSECT' as INDUST_CLASS_CD ,g.GICS_SECTOR_NM as INDUST_NAME ,g.GICS_SECTOR as INDUST_CD ,NULL as SECURITY_ID ,crd.EXTERNAL_SECURITY_IDENTIFIER from T_ODS_SEC s join T_ODS_CRD_SEC crd on s.ODS_SEC_ID = crd.ODS_SEC_ID join T_ODS_REF_GICS g on s.ODS_GICS_ID = g.ODS_GICS_ID and s.BBRG_YELLOW_KEY <> 'Muni' where s.ACTV_FLG = '1' and s.EXT_Sec_ID is not null
union
select 'GICS Sub Industry' as SCHEME_NAME ,'GSIND' as INDUST_CLASS_CD ,g.GICS_SUB_INDUSTRY_NM as INDUST_NAME ,REPLACE(g.GICS_SUB_INDUSTRY, CHAR(10), '') as INDUST_CD ,NULL as SECURITY_ID ,crd.EXTERNAL_SECURITY_IDENTIFIER from T_ODS_SEC s join T_ODS_CRD_SEC crd on s.ODS_SEC_ID = crd.ODS_SEC_ID join T_ODS_REF_GICS g on s.ODS_GICS_ID = g.ODS_GICS_ID where s.ACTV_FLG = '1' and s.EXT_Sec_ID is not null and s.BBRG_YELLOW_KEY <> 'Muni' order by 6,4

(SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI_PFD WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') FI_PFD ON FI_PFD.ODS_SEC_ID=SEC.ODS_SEC_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI_CRNCY WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') FI_CUR ON FI_CUR.ODS_SEC_ID=SEC.ODS_SEC_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN T_ODS_SEC_EQUITY SEC_EQ ON SEC_EQ.ODS_SEC_ID=SEC.ODS_SEC_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT E.CUSIP,E.BLOOMBERG_CMPNY_ID,S.EXT_SEC_ID,S.BBG_UNIQUE_SEC_ID FROM T_ODS_SEC_EQUITY E, T_ODS_SEC S WHERE E.ODS_SEC_ID=S.ODS_SEC_ID AND E.BLOOMBERG_CMPNY_ID_ADR_UNDERLIER IS NULL AND S.EXT_SEC_ID IS LEFT OUTER JOIN T_ODS_REF_SEC_CLASSIFICATION_TYPE CTYPE ON CTYPE.ODS_SEC_CLSSCTN_TYP_ID = SEC_CLASSIFICATION.ODS_SEC_CLSSCTN_TYP_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT BANK_FUND_CD,CLS_CUSIP FROM ODS_SEC_ID,MAX(VOLUME_DATE) VOLUME_DATE from T_ODS_SEC_VOLUME GROUP BY ODS_SEC_ID)V_MB WHERE V.ODS_SEC_ID=V_MB.ODS_SEC_ID AND V.VOLUME_DATE=V_MB.VOLUME_DATE) SEC_VOL ON FI.INDUSTRY_GROUP=REF.INDUST_NAME WHERE FI.ACTV_FLG='1' AND REF.INDUST_CLASS_CD='BBGRP' AND REF.INDUST_CD IS NOT NULL UNION Select REF.INDUST_CD AS INDUST_CD,REF.INDUST_CLASS_CD AS INDUST_CLASS_CD,convert(varchar,EQ.BLOOMBERG_CMPNY_ID) AS ISSUER_CD from T_ODS_SEC_EQUITY EQ LEFT OUTER JOIN T_ODS_REF_CRD_BBG_INDUSTRY_CODES REF ON EQ.INDUSTRY_SUBGROUP=REF.INDUST_NAME where DATA_QUALITY = 'Active' AND REF.INDUST_CLASS_CD='BBSBG' AND REF.INDUST_CD IS NOT NULL UNION select REF.INDUST_CD AS INDUST_CD,REF.INDUST_CLASS_CD AS INDUST_CLASS_CD,convert(varchar,FI.ID_BB_COMPANY) AS ISSUER_CD from T_ODS_SEC_FI FI LEFT OUTER JOIN T_ODS_REF_CRD_BBG_INDUSTRY_CODES REF ON FI.INDUSTRY_SUBGROUP=REF.INDUST_NAME WHERE FI.ACTV_FLG='1' AND REF.INDUST_CLASS_CD='BBSBG' AND REF.INDUST_CD IS NOT NULL UNION Select REF.INDUST_CD AS INDUST_CD,REF.INDUST_CLASS_CD AS INDUST_CLASS_CD,convert(varchar,EQ.BLOOMBERG_CMPNY_ID) AS ISSUER_CD from T_ODS_SEC_EQUITY EQ LEFT OUTER JOIN T_ODS_REF_CRD_BBG_INDUSTRY_CODES REF ON EQ.INDUSTRY_SECTOR=REF.INDUST_NAME where DATA_QUALITY = 'Active' AND REF.INDUST_CLASS_CD='BBSCT' AND REF.INDUST_CD IS NOT NULL UNION select REF.INDUST_CD AS INDUST_CD,REF.INDUST_CLASS_CD AS INDUST_CLASS_CD,convert(varchar,FI.ID_BB_COMPANY) AS ISSUER_CD from (select distinct al.ID_BB_COMPANY ,coalesce(eq.EQY_SIC_CODE,pf.EQY_SIC_CODE,mm.EQY_SIC_CODE,co.EQY_SIC_CODE) AS EQY_SIC_CODE from (SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') al left join (SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI_EQUITY WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') eq on al.ODS_SEC_ID = eq.ODS_SEC_ID left join (SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI_PFD WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') pf on al.ODS_SEC_ID = pf.ODS_SEC_ID left join (SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI_MMKT WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') mm on al.ODS_SEC_ID = mm.ODS_SEC_ID left join (SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI_CORP WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') co on al.ODS_SEC_ID = co.ODS_SEC_ID) FI LEFT OUTER JOIN T_ODS_REF_CRD_BBG_INDUSTRY_CODES REF ON FI.EQY_SIC_CODE=REF.INDUST_CD WHERE REF.INDUST_CLASS_CD='BBSIC' AND REF.INDUST_CD IS NOT NULL UNION Select REF.INDUST_CD AS INDUST_CD,REF.INDUST_CLASS_CD AS INDUST_CLASS_CD,convert(varchar,EQ.BLOOMBERG_CMPNY_ID) AS ISSUER_CD from T_ODS_SEC_EQUITY EQ LEFT OUTER JOIN T_ODS_REF_CRD_BBG_INDUSTRY_CODES REF ON EQ.EQY_SIC_CODE=REF.INDUST_CD where DATA_QUALITY = 'Active' AND REF.INDUST_CLASS_CD='BBSIC' AND REF.INDUST_CD IS NOT NULL UNION select REF.INDUST_CD AS INDUST_CD,REF.INDUST_CLASS_CD AS INDUST_CLASS_CD,convert(varchar,FI.ID_BB_COMPANY) AS ISSUER_CD from T_ODS_SEC_FI FI LEFT OUTER JOIN T_ODS_REF_CRD_BBG_INDUSTRY_CODES REF ON FI.INDUSTRY_SECTOR=REF.INDUST_NAME WHERE FI.ACTV_FLG='1' AND REF.INDUST_CLASS_CD='BBSCT' AND REF.INDUST_CD IS NOT NULL UNION select REF.INDUST_CD AS INDUST_CD,REF.INDUST_CLASS_CD AS INDUST_CLASS_CD,convert(varchar,FI.ID_BB_COMPANY) AS ISSUER_CD from (select distinct al.ID_BB_COMPANY ,coalesce(eq.ISSUER_INDUSTRY,mu.ISSUER_INDUSTRY,pf.ISSUER_INDUSTRY,mm.ISSUER_INDUSTRY,gv.ISSUER_INDUSTRY,co.ISSUER_INDUSTRY) as ISSUER_INDUSTRY from (SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') al left join (SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI_EQUITY WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') eq on al.ODS_SEC_ID = eq.ODS_SEC_ID left join (SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI_MUNI WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') mu on al.ODS_SEC_ID = mu.ODS_SEC_ID left join (SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI_PFD WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') pf on al.ODS_SEC_ID = pf.ODS_SEC_ID left join (SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI_MMKT WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') mm on al.ODS_SEC_ID = mm.ODS_SEC_ID left join (SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI_GOVT WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') gv on al.ODS_SEC_ID = gv.ODS_SEC_ID left join (SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI_CORP WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') co on al.ODS_SEC_ID = co.ODS_SEC_ID left join (SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI_INDEX WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') id on al.ODS_SEC_ID = id.ODS_SEC_ID left join (SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI_MTGE WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') mt on al.ODS_SEC_ID = mt.ODS_SEC_ID) FI LEFT OUTER JOIN T_ODS_REF_CRD_BBG_INDUSTRY_CODES REF ON FI.ISSUER_INDUSTRY=REF.INDUST_NAME WHERE REF.INDUST_CLASS_CD='BBISS' AND REF.INDUST_CD IS NOT NULL UNION select REF.INDUST_CD AS INDUST_CD,REF.INDUST_CLASS_CD AS INDUST_CLASS_CD,convert(varchar,FI.ID_BB_COMPANY) AS ISSUER_CD from (select distinct al.ID_BB_COMPANY ,mu.MUNI_ISSUE_TYP from (SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') al join (SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI_MUNI WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') mu on al.ODS_SEC_ID = mu.ODS_SEC_ID) FI LEFT OUTER JOIN T_ODS_REF_CRD_BBG_INDUSTRY_CODES REF ON WITH CRD_SECURITY AS (select * from T_OUTBD_CRD_SECURITY WITH (NOLOCK)) ,GOVT_SEC AS (select DISTINCT ODS_SEC_ID from T_ODS_CRD_SEC where SECURITY_TYPE_CODE IN ('01','02','03','04'))
select distinct NULL,'MOODY_L' RATER_CD,case when MOODY_L.RTNG is null then 'NR' else MOODY_L.RTNG end as RTNG , cs.EXT_SEC_ID,NULL AS SEC_ID,NULL as RTNG_TYP_CD from CRD_SECURITY cs left join (select * from CRD_SECURITY where RTNG_TYP_CD = 'RTG_MOODY') MOODY_L on cs.ODS_SEC_ID = MOODY_L.ODS_SEC_ID union select distinct NULL,'DBRS_L' RATER_CD,case when DBRS_L.RTNG is null then 'NR' else DBRS_L.RTNG end as RTNG , cs.EXT_SEC_ID,NULL AS SEC_ID,NULL as RTNG_TYP_CD from CRD_SECURITY cs left join (select * from CRD_SECURITY where RTNG_TYP_CD = 'RTG_DBRS') DBRS_L on cs.ODS_SEC_ID = DBRS_L.ODS_SEC_ID union select distinct NULL,'DBRS_CP_S' RATER_CD,case when DBRS_CP_S.RTNG is null then 'NR' else DBRS_CP_S.RTNG end as RTNG , cs.EXT_SEC_ID,NULL AS SEC_ID,NULL as RTNG_TYP_CD from CRD_SECURITY cs left join (select * from CRD_SECURITY where RTNG_TYP_CD = 'RTG_DBRS_ST') DBRS_CP_S on cs.ODS_SEC_ID = DBRS_CP_S.ODS_SEC_ID union select distinct NULL,'FITCH_L' RATER_CD,case when FITCH_L.RTNG is null then 'NR' else FITCH_L.RTNG end as RTNG , cs.EXT_SEC_ID,NULL AS SEC_ID,NULL as RTNG_TYP_CD from CRD_SECURITY cs left join (select * from CRD_SECURITY where RTNG_TYP_CD = 'RTG_FITCH') FITCH_L on cs.ODS_SEC_ID = FITCH_L.ODS_SEC_ID union select distinct NULL,'BLOOMBERG' RATER_CD,case when BLOOMBERG.RTNG is null then 'NR' else BLOOMBERG.RTNG end as RTNG , cs.EXT_SEC_ID,NULL AS SEC_ID,NULL as RTNG_TYP_CD from CRD_SECURITY cs left join (select * from CRD_SECURITY where RTNG_TYP_CD = 'BB_COMPOSITE') BLOOMBERG on cs.ODS_SEC_ID = BLOOMBERG.ODS_SEC_ID union select distinct NULL,'SP_L' RATER_CD,case when SP_L.RTNG is null then 'NR' else SP_L.RTNG end as RTNG , cs.EXT_SEC_ID,NULL AS SEC_ID,NULL as RTNG_TYP_CD from CRD_SECURITY cs left join (select * from CRD_SECURITY where RTNG_TYP_CD = 'RTG_SP') SP_L on cs.ODS_SEC_ID = SP_L.ODS_SEC_ID union select distinct NULL,'INTERNAL_L' RATER_CD ,case when GOVT_SEC.ODS_SEC_ID IS NOT NULL THEN 'AAA' when INTERNAL.RTNG is null then 'NR' else INTERNAL.RTNG end as RTNG , cs.EXT_SEC_ID,NULL AS SEC_ID,NULL as RTNG_TYP_CD from CRD_SECURITY cs left join (select * from CRD_SECURITY where RTNG_TYP_CD = 'INTERNAL') INTERNAL on cs.ODS_SEC_ID = INTERNAL.ODS_SEC_ID left JOIN GOVT_SEC on cs.ODS_SEC_ID=GOVT_SEC.ODS_SEC_ID order by 4

,MAX(COALESCE(FI_EQ.EQY_INIT_PO_DT,SEC_EQ.INITIAL_PUBLIC_OFFERING_DT)) AS OPER_DATE ,MAX(ISS.TOT_ASSETS) AS TOT_ASSETS ,NULL AS SIZ_RANK ,(select ISO_CNTRY_CD from T_ODS_REF_COUNTRY where ODS_CNTRY_ID=MAX(COALESCE(ISS.ODS_CNTRY_OF_DOMICILE_ID,ISS.ODS_CNTRY_OF_INCORPORATION_ID,ISS.ODS_CNTRY_OF_RISK_ID))) AS CNTRY_CD ,NUll AS FD_RESV_MEM ,MAX(ISS.NET_WORTH) AS NET_WORTH ,(CASE WHEN CRNCY_CD FROM T_ODS_REF_CURRENCY WHERE ODS_CRNCY_ID=MAX(SEC.ODS_CRNCY_LOCAL_ID))) AS CRNCY_CD ,NULL AS CUSIP_ROOT ,NULL AS LU_ISSUE_NUMBER ,NULL AS CREDIT_RPT ,NULL AS NEXT_REVIEW_DATE ,NULL AS ANALYST_ID ,NULL AS BIC_CODE ,MAX(COALESCE(FI_EQ.TOTAL_NON_VOTING_SHARES_VALUE,SEC_EQ.TOTAL_NON_VOTING_SHARES)) AS NON_VOTING_SHARES ,NULL AS UDF_FLOAT1 ,NULL AS UDF_FLOAT2 ,NULL AS UDF_FLOAT3 ,NULL AS UDF_FLOAT4 ,NULL AS UDF_FLOAT5 ,NULL AS UDF_FLOAT6 ,NULL AS UDF_FLOAT7 ,NULL AS UDF_FLOAT8 ,NULL AS UDF_FLOAT9 ,NULL AS UDF_FLOAT10 , MAX((CASE WHEN OFAC.ODS_ISSUER_ID IS NULL THEN'1' WHEN OFAC.RECORD_STATUS like '%Matched/Reporting Not Required%' THEN '2' WHEN OFAC.RECORD_STATUS like '%Rev in Progress/Info Pending%' THEN '3' WHEN OFAC.RECORD_STATUS like '%Blank%' THEN '3' END)) --NULL AS UDF_CHAR1 ,NULL AS UDF_CHAR2 ,NULL AS UDF_CHAR3 ,NULL AS UDF_CHAR4 ,NULL AS UDF_CHAR5 ,NULL AS UDF_CHAR6 ,NULL AS UDF_CHAR7 ,NULL AS UDF_CHAR8 ,NULL AS UDF_CHAR9 ,NULL AS UDF_CHAR10 ,NULL AS UDF_DATE1 ,NULL AS UDF_DATE2 ,NULL AS UDF_DATE3 ,NULL AS UDF_DATE4 ,NULL AS UDF_DATE5 ,NULL AS CONTACT_NAME ,NULL AS ADDR1 ,NULL AS ADDR2 ,NULL AS ADDR3 ,NULL AS CITY ,(select T_ODS_REF_US_STATE.US_STATE_CD from T_ODS_REF_US_STATE WHERE ODS_US_STATE_ID=MAX(COALESCE(ISS.ODS_STATE_OF_DOMICILE_ID,ODS_STATE_OF_INCORPORATION_ID))) AS STATE_CD ,NULL AS POSTAL_CD ,NULL AS DTC_NO ,MAX(ISS.BBG_CMPNY_ID) AS BB_COMPANY_ID ,NULL AS EXT_SEC_ID ,NULL AS MARKIT_VALID_FROM ,NULL AS MARKIT_VALID_TO ,NULL AS NEXT_RED_CD ,NULL AS PREV_RED_CD ,NULL AS JURISDICTION ,NULL AS RED_CD ,MAX(ISS.BIC_INDUSTRY_GROUP_NAME) AS BIC_INDUSTRY_GROUP_NAME ,NULL AS BIC_INDUST_GROUP_ID ,NULL AS BIC_INDUSTRY_GROUP_CD ,NULL AS BIC_INDUSTRY_GROUP_RANK_ID ,MAX(ISS.BIC_INDUSTRY_SUBGROUP_NAME) AS BIC_INDUSTRY_SUBGROUP_NAME ,NULL AS BIC_INDUSTRY_SUBGROUP_ID ,NULL AS BIC_INDSUTRY_SUBGROUP_CD ,NULL AS BIC_INDUSTRY_SUBGROUP_RANK_ID ,MAX(ISS.BIC_INDUSTRY_SECTOR_1_NAME) AS BIC_INDUSTRY_SECTOR_1_NAME ,NULL AS BIC_INDUSTRY_SECTOR_1_ID ,NULL AS BIC_INDUSTRY_SECTOR_1_CD ,NULL AS BIC_INDUSTRY_SECTOR_1_RANK_ID ,NULL AS BIC_INDUSTRY_SECTOR_2_NAME ,NULL AS BIC_INDUSTRY_SECTOR_2_ID ,NULL AS BIC_INDUSTRY_SECTOR_2_CD ,NULL AS BIC_INDUSTRY_SECTOR_2_RANK_ID ,MAX(COALESCE(FI_CORP.ISSUER_INDUSTRY,FI_EQ.ISSUER_INDUSTRY,FI_GVT.ISSUER_INDUSTRY,FI_MMKT.ISSUER_INDUSTRY,FI_MUNI.ISSUER_INDUSTRY,FI_PFD.ISSUER_INDUSTRY)) AS BIC_INDUSTRY_ISSUER_NAME ,NULL AS BIC_ISSUER_INDUSTRY_ID ,NULL AS BIC_ISSUER_INDUSTRY_CD ,NULL AS BIC_ISSUER_INDUSTRY_RANK_ID ,MAX(FI_MUNI.MUNI_ISSUE_TYP) AS BIC_MUNI_ISSUE_TYP_NAME ,NULL AS BIC_MUNI_ISSUE_TYP_ID ,NULL AS BIC_MUNI_ISSUE_TYP_CD ,NULL AS BIC_MUNI_ISSUE_TYP_RANK_ID ,MAX(FI_MUNI.MUNI_LONG_INDUSTRY_TYP) AS BIC_MUNI_LONG_INDUSTRY_TYP_NAME ,NULL AS BIC_MUNI_LONG_INDUSTRY_TYP_ID ,NULL AS BIC_MUNI_LONG_INDUSTRY_TYP_CD ,NULL AS BIC_MUNI_LONG_INDUSTRY_TYP_RANK_ID ,MAX(ISS.RATER_CD) AS RATER_CD ,MAX(ISS.RATING_CD) AS RATING_CD from T_ODS_ISSUER ISS LEFT OUTER JOIN T_ODS_SEC SEC ON SEC.ODS_ISSUER_ID=ISS.ODS_ISSUER_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI_MUNI WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') FI_MUNI ON FI_MUNI.ODS_SEC_ID=SEC.ODS_SEC_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') FI ON FI.ODS_SEC_ID=SEC.ODS_SEC_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI_CORP WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') FI_CORP ON FI_CORP.ODS_SEC_ID=SEC.ODS_SEC_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI_EQUITY WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') FI_EQ ON FI_EQ.ODS_SEC_ID=SEC.ODS_SEC_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI_INDEX WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') FI_IDX ON FI_IDX.ODS_SEC_ID=SEC.ODS_SEC_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI_COMDTY WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') FI_CMDTY ON FI_CMDTY.ODS_SEC_ID=SEC.ODS_SEC_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI_GOVT WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') FI_GVT ON FI_GVT.ODS_SEC_ID=SEC.ODS_SEC_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI_MMKT WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') FI_MMKT ON FI_MMKT.ODS_SEC_ID=SEC.ODS_SEC_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI_MTGE WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') FI_MTGE ON FI_MTGE.ODS_SEC_ID=SEC.ODS_SEC_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT * FROM T_ODS_SEC_FI_PFD WHERE ACTV_FLG='1') FI_PFD ON FI_PFD.ODS_SEC_ID=SEC.ODS_SEC_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN T_ODS_SEC_FI_CRNCY FI_CUR ON FI_CUR.ODS_SEC_ID=SEC.ODS_SEC_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN T_ODS_SEC_EQUITY SEC_EQ ON SEC_EQ.ODS_SEC_ID=SEC.ODS_SEC_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN T_ODS_REF_CRD_INDUSTRY CRD_IND ON CRD_IND.CRD_INDUSTRY= ISS.ISSUER_TYP_CD LEFT OUTER JOIN T_ODS_ISSUER_OFAC OFAC ON OFAC.CUSTOMER_NAME = ISS.ISSUER_LONG_NM GROUP BY BBG_CMPNY_ID

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
WITH CTE_AVG AS ( select avg(CAST(BATCH_DURATION AS DECIMAL)) AVG_BATCH_DURATION ,batch_id from ( select *,ROW_NUMBER() over(partition by batch_id order by Start_dt desc) as rownum from T_CFW_BATCH_RUN where BATCH_DURATION IS NOT NULL )z where z.rownum<=30 GROUP BY z.batch_id ), CTE_FIRST_RUN AS ( select A.BATCH_ID,A.BATCH_DURATION AS FIRST_RUN_DURATION from T_CFW_BATCH_RUN A INNER JOIN ( select min(START_DT) AS START_DT,batch_id from T_CFW_BATCH_RUN where YEAR(START_DT)=YEAR(GETDATE()) AND BATCH_DURATION IS NOT NULL GROUP BY batch_id )B ON A.BATCH_ID=B.BATCH_ID AND A.START_DT=B.START_DT ),
CTE_FINAL AS ( select CTE_AVG.BATCH_ID,CTE_AVG.AVG_BATCH_DURATION, CTE_FIRST_RUN.FIRST_RUN_DURATION from CTE_AVG LEFT OUTER JOIN CTE_FIRST_RUN ON CTE_AVG.BATCH_ID=CTE_FIRST_RUN.BATCH_ID )
SELECT z.BATCH_RUN_ID, z.BATCH_ID, z.STATUS_ID, z.START_DT, z.PROCESS_COUNT , CTE_FINAL.AVG_BATCH_DURATION, CTE_FINAL.FIRST_RUN_DURATION FROM ( SELECT A.BATCH_RUN_ID, A.BATCH_ID, A.STATUS_ID, A.START_DT, (SELECT COUNT (C.PROCESS_ID) AS PROCESS_COUNT FROM T_CFW_PROCESS C, T_CFW_PROCESS_RUN B WHERE C.PROCESS_ID = B.PROCESS_ID AND C.PROCESS_TYPE_ID = 13 AND B.STATUS_ID = 13 AND B.BATCH_RUN_ID = $$MV_BATCH_RUN_ID AND C.PARENT_BATCH_ID = $$BATCH_ID GROUP BY B.BATCH_RUN_ID, C.PARENT_BATCH_ID) AS PROCESS_COUNT FROM T_CFW_BATCH_RUN A, T_CFW_BATCH B WHERE A.BATCH_ID = B.BATCH_ID AND A.BATCH_ID = $$BATCH_ID AND A.STATUS_ID = 11 AND A.BATCH_RUN_ID = $$MV_BATCH_RUN_ID AND B.NAME = '$$WKFL_NAME' )z LEFT OUTER JOIN CTE_FINAL ON z.BATCH_ID=CTE_FINAL.BATCH_ID
